title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - USA - Little Rock - Little Rock Central High School
description:
In this video we will fly over the Little Rock Central High School . Little Rock Central High School (LRCHS) is an accredited comprehensive public high school in Little Rock, Arkansas, United States. The school was the site of forced desegregation in 1957 after the U.S. Supreme Court ruled that segregation of public schools was unconstitutional three years earlier. This was during the period of heightened activism in the civil rights movement.
